the magnetic field coming in

00:00:27.890 --> 00:00:31.850
this direction on this arm
of the wire or the

00:00:31.850 --> 00:00:34.520
circuit is net downwards.

00:00:34.520 --> 00:00:36.510
And on this arm, it
was net upwards.

00:00:36.510 --> 00:00:39.750
And so it provided a net
torque on this circuit.

