was the former right
hand side.

00:04:17.125 --> 00:04:20.380
It's still going in that
upwards direction.

00:04:20.380 --> 00:04:22.800
So when you take the cross
product, what is going to be

00:04:22.800 --> 00:04:25.230
the net magnetic
field on that?

00:04:25.230 --> 00:04:27.660
Or the force of the
magnetic field?

00:04:27.660 --> 00:04:31.050
Well, you do the same
right hand rule.

00:04:31.050 --> 00:04:32.730
Point your index finger up.

00:04:32.730 --> 00:04:34.170
Put your middle finger
in the direction of

00:04:34.170 --> 00:04:35.680
the magnetic field.

00:04:35.680 --> 00:04:38.120
This is the palm, this is
your other two fingers.

