configuration.

00:05:56.510 --> 00:06:00.220
Maybe you go all the way back
to this configuration, where

00:06:00.220 --> 00:06:04.580
it's essentially a complete
180 degree turn.

00:06:04.580 --> 00:06:08.260
And then since on this side
the current's going to be

00:06:08.260 --> 00:06:10.360
going up and on this side the
current's going down, because

00:06:10.360 --> 00:06:14.060
you've essentially flipped
this thing over, then the

00:06:14.060 --> 00:06:17.120
effect of the magnetic field is
going to say, well, upwards

00:06:17.120 --> 00:06:19.540
on the left, downwards
on the right.

00:06:19.540 --> 00:06:20.900
And so it's going to
turn the other way.

00:06:20.900 --> 00:06:23.920
So if you think about it, it's
going to keep oscillating.

