either have to reverse the

00:06:37.840 --> 00:06:41.330
current once you get into this
configuration, or either turn

00:06:41.330 --> 00:06:42.380
off the magnetic field.

00:06:42.380 --> 00:06:46.630
Or maybe you could reverse the
magnetic field to get it going

00:06:46.630 --> 00:06:47.510
in the other direction.

00:06:47.510 --> 00:06:49.540
And actually you have another
problem, which is a slightly

00:06:49.540 --> 00:06:52.730
lesser problem, is if this was
a circuit and you just kept

00:06:52.730 --> 00:06:55.770
turning over and over the
circuit, the wires would get

00:06:55.770 --> 00:06:56.280
twisted here.

00:06:56.280 --> 00:06:58.430
So you couldn't do
it indefinitely.

